      "time": "00:00:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, this is my mother, and this is my father.",
      "zh": "嗯，這是我媽媽，這是我爸爸。",
      "ja": "ええと、これは私の母で、こちらは父です。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How old is your mother?",
      "zh": "你媽媽幾歲？",
      "ja": "あなたのお母さんは何歳ですか？",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She is 45 years old.",
      "zh": "她45歲。",
      "ja": "彼女は45歳です。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What is her name?",
