      "ja": "彼女の名前は何ですか？",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Her name is Mary.",
      "zh": "她叫瑪麗。",
      "ja": "彼女の名前はメアリーです。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How old is your father?",
