      "time": "00:02:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You have a nice family.",
      "zh": "你有個好家庭。",
      "ja": "素敵な家族ですね。",
      "time": "00:02:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks. You look nice in this picture.",
      "zh": "謝謝。你在這張照片裡看起來很好看。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。この写真のあなたは素敵に見えます。",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What would you like to have?",
      "zh": "你想喝什麼？",
